{"tid":2149704,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"有測量師倡防疫角度解決住屋問題 仿效日本避難手冊","createTime":"2020-08-10T13:58:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-10T14:21:40.000Z","uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b5ee4769de06b999da51c778a86e8b224aa54575","tid":2149704,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T13:58:48.000Z","msg":"有測量師倡防疫角度解決住屋問題 仿效日本避難手冊<br />\n2020-08-10 HKT 15:35<br />\n<br />\n&quot;其中測量師學會規劃及發展組主席林家輝表示......香港需要從防疫角度，解決住屋問題，例如政府帶頭大規模使用組裝合成建築法興建房屋，滿足市民的房屋需求。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n&quot;林家輝又說，面對有大廈出現確診者時，可以仿效日本制定避難手冊，利用社區內的學校或社區會堂作避難所，放置至少7日的糧食、藥物及被鋪等，萬一發生事故，居民毋須等候政府安排，即可到安全地方暫避。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542871-20200810.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542871-20200810.htm&d=6XXjbPj9602%2BpZUfgYO1mDIStCm0mHK7%2Bbmf%2BnNiY0c%3D&h=645ff0d4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542871-20200810.htm&h=af7f5c93\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542871-20200810.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\"><strong>Good idea<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"d32282ed6d2129c138d54448ac51a25a600b50c0","tid":2149704,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T14:01:06.000Z","msg":"一人一個籠，咪得囉"},{"pid":"87d7dcbe4d83b6136159e515d41c2efe76352e13","tid":2149704,"uid":252142,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T14:21:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}